doc_summary_long: St. Louis' health department uses barber shops to fight STDs In some St. Louis barber shops and beauty salons, customers might get sex education while having their hair cut and styled. The health department has recruited more than a dozen of the shops to help in the fight against the city's high rate of sexually transmitted diseases.
